sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor DomainSvc as UpstreamDomainService
actor User as EndUser
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant NotifyCtrl as NotificationController
participant NotifySvc as NotificationService
participant NotifyDb as MongoNotification
participant Realtime as RealtimeHub
participant Client as WebClient
DomainSvc->>Gateway: POST /api/notifications (internal token)
Gateway->>NotifyCtrl: createNotification
NotifyCtrl->>NotifySvc: validate internal auth + payload
alt Internal token hop le
  NotifySvc->>NotifyDb: insert notification
  NotifySvc->>Realtime: emit notification:new
  NotifySvc-->>DomainSvc: 201 created
else Token sai/thieu
  NotifySvc-->>DomainSvc: 401/403
end
User->>Client: Mo trang thong bao
Client->>Gateway: GET /api/notifications
Gateway->>NotifyCtrl: getUserNotifications
NotifySvc->>NotifyDb: query by userId + paging
NotifySvc-->>Client: list notifications
User->>Client: Mark read all
Client->>Gateway: PATCH /api/notifications/read-all
NotifySvc->>NotifyDb: set isRead=true + readAt
NotifySvc->>Realtime: emit notification:read_all
